snippet.title: "FNaF: Where Dreams DIE" Official GameJolt Trailer
snippet.description:
https://gamejolt.com/games/WhereDreamsDIE/844276

You will feel the "Enhanced" Five Nights at Freddy's experience full of fear and terror. 

After some incidents that happened years ago, everything was settled and closed. However, a company that wanted to keep the legend of "Freddy Fazbear's Pizza" alive collected everything that was left and created a museum. But there was something they forgot. There was another person deep inside, forgotten and waiting to be rescued. He should have taken a revenge.
#fangame #fnaf #horror 

Music from #InAudio: https://inaudio.org/ 
Nightmare.

@TheFarlander
